window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The war between Dicathen and Alacrya is over and Arthur Leywin has vanished. </b></p> <p>In the uncertain aftermath of this decisive loss, a few familiar faces navigate peril–both political and moral–as they are now forced to make a difficult choice: accept life under Vritra rule or keep fighting despite impossible odds? As Dicathen falls, Mica Earthborn, Lilia Helstea, Emily Watsken, and Jasmine Flamesworth must each answer this question for themselves.</p> <p>To get the best listening experience, <i>Amongst the Fallen </i>should be listened to after book eight of The Beginning After the End series.</p>"; 
